## Our Promise

WaitingTheLongest.com is dedicated to giving visibility to dogs who need it most. We track wait times, monitor euthanasia lists, and highlight the dogs who are running out of time.

Every dog featured here has a story. Every one of them deserves a chance.

Will you be part of their happy ending?

